snippet.title: Key Hunters DX - SAGE 2020 Trailer
snippet.description:
Key Hunters DX is a remake of the original Sonic & Knuckles Key Hunters fangame made by Illias Studio in association with Cosmic Shockwave. This fangame puts a twist on things by changing the objective of the stages to be akin to the Emerald Radar stages for Knuckles in the Sonic Adventure Series. It boasts some new and returning features and sets out to be a improved and polished experience.

Download the SAGE Demo as well as various older builds here!
https://sites.google.com/view/sonic-project-twisted/homepage

Disclaimer :
Key Hunters DX is in no way affiliated with Sega or Sonic Team. Its a non profit project created by fans of the original series
